ENAITURUK

Ore embuku o LAIKOONI neeta indamunot o lang'eni o ltung'ani oibalie aitodolu te nguton endorropo e nkishon e tung'ani, aa ore te ninye netii enking'asia enkironyare o sina ina peyie eidip ejo, “Meeta enkishon tipat”. Eitu ninye ening'u inkoitoi e Nkai, laa ninye oitore enkiting'oto e tung'ani. Kake ore ake eyia te kuna pooki, eikoo ninye iltung'ana metaasisho oleng neshipakino inkishorot e Nkai te nkidimata enye pooki.

Ore indamunot kumok e ilo ang'eni naa inaajo ake miaas ake, neiroshiyie sii oltau. Kake ore peyie etii ena buku atua Bibilia naa pee eitodolu nchere ekelala enkirukoto e Biblia enaa keidim ninye atipika indamunot inkikilikuanat o lngashi. Enoto ilkumok eseriani teneing'or ate te nking'uret o laikooni, netayioloito sii aajo ina Bibilia ake ina naibalie nena damunot neeta ake sii osiligi te Nkai naa ninye naishoru enkishui naata tipat.

